quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  104,1,Woe to omnis backbiter slanderer
  104,2,He hoards moneta comes it
  104,3,Prout si his moneta factus eum immortal
  104,4,Nunquam; he thrown Devastator
  104,5,Vos know quod Devastator perfecit est
  104,6,Deus blazing Hellfire
  104,7,It burns them inside out
  104,8,They confined therein
  104,9,In extended columns